description:
This set of weapons features cute moogle-inspired designs for each of the different tribes. *The tribe that can use each weapon is noted in brackets below.
- Mogcalibur (Clavat only)
- Mogungnir (Lilty only)
- Kupo Kupo Hammer (Yuke only)
- Kupo Kupo Racket (Selkie only)
name: Moogle Weapon Pack
